Cats are playful creatures that need mental and physical stimulation. Providing a variety of toys can keep them entertained and prevent boredom. Here are five cat toys that your feline friend will love. Feather wands are a classic favorite. They mimic the movement of birds and engage your cat’s hunting instincts.
